formula: a(n) = sum of the n-th row of A186716.
xref: Connected regular graphs of any degree with girth at least g: A005177 (g=3), A186724 (g=4), A186725 (g=5), this sequence (g=6), A186727 (g=7), A186728 (g=8), A186729 (g=9).
Connected k-regular simple graphs with girth at least 6: this sequence (any k), A186716 (triangle); specific k: A185116 (k=2), A014374 (k=3), A058348 (k=4).
